data.description: Just a golf cart ride away from downtown Ocean Springs, this home on prestigious Iberville Drive has so much space and is a great remodeling opportunity!  Very large family room, open kitchen with walk in pantry, formal living room, two other rooms that could be additional bedrooms and a large screened porch.  Storage shed in back, fenced in yard with lot of fruit trees. HVAC system and ductwork only 2 years old and new Pex plumbing in the house.  This home is ready for your renovations and updates. Come take a look and see the possibilities!
